17. How to increase efficiency of incremental backup and data pump job ?

=> BCT parameter (Block change tracking)
👉 V$BLOCK_CHANGE_TRACKING - if it's enable then incremental backup will be faster way.

👉 SYNTAX :  SELECT STATUS, FILENAME, BYTES, BLOCK_SIZE FROM V$BLOCK_CHANGE_TRACKING;
